dialogueSequence.sentence: What have you done?!
Sir, I’m sorry.  Rufus got over excited and-
Bark bark (My name is NOT Rufus!)
The dog can talk?
He can talk?
Grrr (Of course I can talk.)
Can you understand him?
Nope.
That’s beyond the point.
You’ve killed my favorite pet with the aid of my assistant. Both of you must be punished.
Woah, that thing was more of a problem than a pet!
I raised him since he was naught but a droplet.
He showed me more respect than you ever did.
I sent you away because you did nothing but hinder my research.
What are you talking about, I gave my all to further your research!
Silence!
With the power of the Red Macguffin I’ll-
Thank god you roasted him before he could drop that sick burn.
But did you have to kill him?
He might’ve gone insane after finding that stone, but he was a pure soul.
Bark Bork (I mean, if you didn’t respect your elders then why should they respect you?)
